  [error] Cannot use `?` on `Partial`
   ╭─[test.lis:4:3]
 3 │   let p: Partial<int, string> = Partial.Ok(42)
 4 │   p?
   ·   ─┬
   ·    ╰── `Partial` requires explicit `match`
 5 │ }
   ╰────
  help: The `?` operator is incompatible with `Partial` because it has three variants. Use `match` to handle `Ok`, `Err`, and `Both` explicitly · code: [infer.propagate_on_partial]
